"```sql\nSELECT disp.disp_id\nFROM trans\nJOIN disp ON trans.account_id = disp.account_id\nWHERE trans.amount = 5100\n  AND trans.date = '1998-09-02';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `disp_id` from the `disp` table by joining it with the `trans` table on the `account_id`. It filters the transactions to find the one with an amount of 5100 USD that occurred on the date 1998-09-02."